blocks.en:
flowchart TD
  A[CCM arrives] --> B{level vs MEP}
  B -->|equal| C[MEPprocessEqualCCM]
  B -->|low| D[MEPprocessLowCCM: set xconCCMreceived]
  C --> E{MAID match?}
  E -->|no| F[set xconCCMreceived]
  E -->|yes| G{MEPID & interval ok?}
  G -->|no| H[set errorCCMreceived]
  G -->|yes| I[copy recvd fields, set rCCMreceived]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
  A[CCM 到达] --> B{相对 MEP 的等级}
  B -->|同级| C[MEPprocessEqualCCM]
  B -->|低级| D[MEPprocessLowCCM: 置位 xconCCMreceived]
  C --> E{MAID 匹配?}
  E -->|否| F[置位 xconCCMreceived]
  E -->|是| G{MEPID 与间隔正确?}
  G -->|否| H[置位 errorCCMreceived]
  G -->|是| I[复制 recvd 字段, 置位 rCCMreceived]
